086b38baf729231756cacd752462e1edce080e3d.query:
-- GET ENTITY'S DATA 
        select entity_data from entity 
        where public_key = $1

63ca4e8c83a466081e23dedf11a44dff06f32822.query:
-- GET ENTITY 
        select password, admin from user_account  
        where username=$1

9621947d86f15926728df2e8e8917297c930bd4f.query:
-- UPSERT VALUE
            insert into entity(public_key, entity_data)
            values($1, $2)
            on conflict(public_key, entity_data) do update
            set entity_data = entity.entity_data || $2
